  "text": "Histopathologic examination of endoscopic paraffin-embedded tissue sections was performed by a single pathologist (MA) blinded as to each dog's history and clinical course. Tissues were graded for severity of intestinal mucosal inflammation using simplified WSAVA histopathologic criteria [CITATION_1] .",
